AYOZAADDOHU FEEMAB TADA-A' WA LAA WALIYYUN MENAZ ZULLE FAYURFEDAHU FEEMAA SANA-A' FASUBHAANAHU SUBHAANAHU LAW KAANA FEEHEMAA AALEHATUN ILLAL LAAHO LAFASADATAA WA TAFATTARATAA SUBHAANAL LAAHIL WAHEDIL AHADIS SAMADIL LAZE LAM YALID WA LAM YOOLAD WA LAM YAKUN LAHU KOFOWAN AHADUN ALHAMDO LILLAAHE HAMDAN YO-A'ADELO HAMDA MALAAA-EKATEHIL MOQARRABEENA WA AMBEYAAA-EHIL MURSALEENA WA SALLAL LAAHO A'LAA KHEYARATEHI MOHAMMADIN KHAATAMIN NABIYYEENA WA AALEHIT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENAL MUKHLASEENA WA SALLAMA.\r\n\r\nThe Imam (a.s.) then besought Almighty Allah so earnestly that his eyes shed tears. He then said:\r\n\r\nALLAAHUMMAJ A'LNEE AKHSAAKA KA-ANNEE ARAAKA WA AS-I'DNEE BETAQWAAKA WA LAA TUSHQENEE BEMA'SEYATEKA WA KHIRLEE FEE QAZAAA-EKA WA BAARIK LEE FEE QADAREKA HATTAA LAA OHIBBA TA'JEELA MAA AKHKHARTA WA LAA TAAKHEERA MAA A'JJALTA ALLAAHUMMAJ A'L GHENAAYA FEE NAFSEE WAL YAQEENA FEE QALBEE WAL-IKHLAASA FEE A'MALEE WAN NOORA FEE BASAREE WAL-BASEERATA FEE DEENEE WA MATTE'NEE BEJAWAAREHEE WAJ-A'L SAM-E'E WA BASARIL WAARESEENA MINNEE WAN SURNEE A'LAA MAN ZALAMANEE WA ARENEE FEEHE SAAREE WA MAAA-REBEE WA AQIRRA BEZAALEKA A'YNEE ALLAAHUMMAK SHIF KURBATEE WAS-TUR A'WRATEE WAGHFIR LEE KHATEE-A'TEE WAKH-SAA SHAYTAANEE WA FUKKA REHAANEE WAJ-A'L LEE YAA ELAAHID DARAJATAL U'LYAA FIL AAKHERATE WAL-OOLAA ALLAAHUMMA LAKAL HAMDO KAMAA KHALAQTANEE FA-JA-A'LTANEE SAMEE-A'N BASEERAN WA LAKAL HAMDO KAMAA KHALAQTANEE FA-JA-A'LTANEE KHALQAN SAWIYYAN RAHMATAN BEE WA QAD KUNTA A'N KHALQEE GHANIYYAN RABBE BEMAA BARAATANEE FA-A'DDALTA FITRATEE RABBE BEMAA ANSHAATANEE FA-AHSANTA SOORATEE RABBE BEMAA AHSANTA ELAYYA WA FEE NAFSEE A'AFAYTANEE RABBE BEMAA KALAATANEE WA WAFFAQTANEE RABBE BEMAA AN-A'MTA A'LAYYA FAHADAYTANEE RABBE BEMAA AWLAYTANEE WA MIN KULLE KHAYRIN\r\n\r\nA-A'TAYTANEE RABBE BEMAA A-TA'TANEE WA SAQAYTANEE RABBE BEMAA AGHNAYTANEE WA AQNAYTANEE RABBE BEMAA A-A'NTANEE WA A-A'ZAZTANEE RABBE BEMAA ALBASTANEE MIN SITREKAS SAAFEE WA YASSARTA LEE MIN SUN-E'KAL KAAFEE SALLE A'LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE